parameters.name: 猛獣の鳴き声（低いうなり声）

parameters:
\n<Deorc>"Hahaha! Is that all you've got? There are still more
enemies to face!"

\n<Deorc>"Kuhahaha! What's the matter, suffering on your own? It's
really fun to torment you!"

\n<??>"...Lord, please grant me the power of justice. Strike down
the wicked souls bearing your name, and show me the light to
guide my friends."

\n<??>"In the name of the God of Light, I shall deliver
punishment! O God who governs death and impure souls, let
your body be scorched by the blade of light!!"

\n<??>"Back off, Roselitte! I'm going to get serious for a
moment!"

\n<Ameria>"I'm sorry... I promised to protect you, but I got scared
and ran away again..."

\n<Ameria>"But it's okay now. This time for sure, I will protect you,
Roselitte-san!"

\n<Lyric>"That's just how she is, can't help it. You should just
quietly accept being helped."

\n<Lyric>"Oh, and don't get the wrong idea. I came back for Ameria's
sake. I couldn't care less about you, knight."

\n<Roselitte>"I am one of the Twelve Knights of the Guard! I refuse to do
something as shameful as borrowing the power of civilians or
monsters!"

\n<Roselitte>"I alone am enough for an opponent of this level! Just
listen to me and escape quickly!"
\n<Roselitte>"Don't make me...! Don't make me suffer any more shame...!!"
Lyric placed a wedding ring in Roselitte's palm.
\n<Roselitte>"Th-this is Lord Yuri's! How on earth did you...?"

\n<Lyric>"I happened to find it in that cave where the bandits were.
It's something important to you, right? I thought I'd use it
to blackmail you if necessary, so I've been hiding it all
this time."
\n<Roselitte>"You... what kind of person are you..."

\n<Roselitte>"But thank you... Ah, I'm so relieved... I thought it was
lost forever..."

\n<Lyric>"It's frustrating to not be able to fight alone, to not have
things go your way..."

\n<Lyric>"Feeling pathetic for needing someone's help, feeling
miserable, embarrassed, and scared... Am I wrong?"

\n<Lyric>"This isn't how it was supposed to be. I'm stronger than
this. I can do more."

\n<Lyric>"...But I can't. And when that keeps piling up, I feel like
I'm losing sight of myself."

\n<Lyric>"I'm the same as you. Now, I can hardly fight on my own.
It's miserable, and I start to hate myself."

\n<Lyric>"...But what can we do about it when we're troubled? There's
no use worrying."
\n<Lyric>"Just give up. And accept it... We are weak."

\n<Roselitte>"I can't afford to stop here...! There are still things I
must do...!"

\n<Lyric>"That's right. Even if we're weak, we can't afford to stop.
We still have things we must do."

\n<Lyric>"That ring. You have someone you want to save, right? Then
no matter how shameful or whatever it is, you've got to do
anything for their sake."
\n<Lyric>"...Here's a piece of advice from a senior to you."

\n<Lyric>"Relying on others isn't such a bad thing. Especially if
it's that person behind you."

\n<Ameria>"...If even just a little bit, if I can be of any help to
you, I would be more than happy to support you."
\n<Ameria>"Because for me, Roselitte-san is an incredible person."

\n<Ameria>"You possess strength that I don't have. Brave and noble...
Fighting alongside someone like you has made me very happy
and proud..."

\n<Ameria>"'As a healer, one must be prepared to hold lives in their
hands and take full responsibility to heal once they've said
they would.'"
\n<Ameria>"...So please, let me fight with you."
\n<Deorc>"You bastards... You've really done it now!"

\n<Deorc>"No more mercy! Hey you, how long are you going to play
around?! Hurry up and kill them!!"
\n<Roselitte>"Ameria, Lyric... Will you lend me your strength?"
\n<Lyric>"Hehehe. You're a bit late in getting motivated!"

\n<Deorc>"Enough with the chatter! This is the end for you,
Roselitte!!"
\n<Roselitte>"This is where the real battle starts!!"
\n<Ameria>"We won... we won, we won! Hallelujah!!"
\n<Deorc>"No way... I can't believe I lost...!"

\n<Deorc>"Fine, bring it on! But you haven't forgotten, right!? How
you couldn't lay a finger on me!"

\n<Roselitte>"...Indeed, as I am now, I might not be able to defeat you.
But--"
\n<Deorc>"Tch... annoying brats! Then I'll take on all of you--!"

\n<Deorc>"You... don't get in my way! I'm about to finish these guys
off--!"
\n<??>"Are you going to make me repeat myself? Get going."

\n<??>"Whoa... don't be in such a hurry, Roselitte. You'll see him
again soon enough."

\n<??>"Now, now, no need to make such a scary face. I have no
intention of doing anything to you all right now, so please
relax."

\n<??>"...Well, telling you to relax might be asking too much.
It's okay to be on guard. Just don't attack me out of the
blue, okay?"
\n<??>"Nfufu... I just came to see your faces this time."
The woman said that as she gazed behind Roselitte.

\n<??>"Hey there. Good to see you're doing well. I'm very happy to
see you're trying your best."
\n<??>"But you seem quite tired... You should rest a bit."

\n<Lyric>"...No way. I don't know someone like that. But... maybe
that person is..."
\n<Ameria>"I'm okay... just a little... tired... that's... all..."
